00:04:05.130 --> 00:04:08.910
that the attackers don't go
directly to banking websites,

00:04:08.910 --> 00:04:11.200
Google, social networks and try
to break past all of our

00:04:11.200 --> 00:04:13.360
security layers because
we have lots.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:16.660
