00:04:50.490 --> 00:04:51.470
I can't pay the hotel bill.

00:04:51.470 --> 00:04:52.580
I know we haven't
talked a while.

00:04:52.580 --> 00:04:54.530
Will you wire me money?

00:04:54.530 --> 00:04:55.760
And people do.

00:04:55.760 --> 00:04:56.640
It's embarrassing for them.

00:04:56.640 --> 00:04:58.390
They lose a lot of money.

00:04:58.390 --> 00:04:59.160
It's embarrassing for you.

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:00.500
Your friends are tricked.

00:05:00.500 --> 00:05:02.410
And this is because
of password reuse.

00:05:02.410 --> 00:05:05.590
