00:05:07.970 --> 00:05:10.420
And I don't know about you all,
but I'm embarrassed if

00:05:10.420 --> 00:05:12.580
that's the best advice
we can give.

00:05:12.580 --> 00:05:14.990
And so this is where Google and
other companies are trying

00:05:14.990 --> 00:05:18.400
to help websites move away from
that model into using

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:19.400
identity providers.

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:23.590
