with that sort of puce,

00:09:04.215 --> 00:09:06.810
whatever favorite color.

00:09:06.810 --> 00:09:10.080
So what you're seeing there is
one click sign in with the aid

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:10.920
of an identity provider.

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:13.040
Now, Account Chooser, as Eric
