or something like

00:13:33.780 --> 00:13:35.780
that, it would all fit
together that way.

00:13:35.780 --> 00:13:36.530
ERIC SACHS: Yup.

00:13:36.530 --> 00:13:38.740
TIM BRAY: So that's kind of a
